				"&6&nGear Progression Overview&r"
				""
				"High-tier weapons and armor are locked behind specific boss milestones. This questline will guide you through the progression system so you can unlock better equipment tiers."
				""
				"The Armageddon mod completely overhauls vanilla progression, introducing custom mechanics and unique tiers of ores to discover as you advance."
				""
				"Every boss features unique combat gimmicks, meaning &nproper preparation&r is vital before jumping into the fight. Take your time, gear up, and don't rush in unprepared."
