			description: [
				"&6&nGold Tier Progression&r"
				""
				"Just like with iron, unlocking the use of gold ingots requires you to track down and"
				"[gap=0]"
				"&cdefeat The Goblin Lord&r."
				""
				"This boss inflicts multiple heavy debuffs whenever he lands a hit, making it crucial to time your dodges carefully and avoid his direct attacks."
				""
				"During the fight, he will summon minions that deal massive damage, potentially hitting harder than the boss itself, but they have very low health. Use this to your advantage and prioritize clearing out the summons quickly before they overwhelm you."
